attribs.name: proficiencies
attribs.current: Weapons:  Longsword, Shortsword, Longbow, Shortbow, simple weapons

attribs.name: miscellaneous_notes
attribs.current:
Full Name:  Elinara Prill
Cursed to endure labor pains every nine months until she accepts birthing the Sidhe child.

attribs.name: personality_traits
attribs.current:
Defiant. I did not *ask* to be chosen or for the task thrust upon me. I refuse to do something by force.

Honorable. Despite being tricked, I still believe in honor. When I give my word, I keep it, but I don't give it easily.

attribs.name: ideals
attribs.current: Contrary. I hate this task and I did not agree to be obedient to this entity.

attribs.name: bonds
attribs.current: Opportunistic. I will dedicate myself to those who are useful to helping me hide from the Queen, discover a cure to my curse, or to those I've given my word.

attribs.name: flaws
attribs.current: Paranoid. I've been running from a powerful being who I have defied and I have no idea who is helping her.

attribs.name: repeating_spell0_-KgYIgNY2o2GEn1ohljW_content
attribs.current:
*Psionic Talent*
Psychically strike one visible creature within 120ft. Damage increases by 1d8 at 5th, 11th, and 17th lvl.

attribs.name: repeating_spell1_-KgYIgNZywkp4Qkd1Lgp_content
attribs.current:
*Lesser Discipline (Intellect Fortress)*
*Cost:  1 psi point*

Impose disadvantage on one attack roll made against you if you can see the attacker. If the attack still hits, attacker takes psychic damage equal to half mystic level (rounded up).

attribs.name: repeating_spell0_-KgYIgNZfk0VWX8aSuZa_materials
attribs.current: an item that is native to the Feywild

attribs.name: repeating_spell0_-KgYIgNZfk0VWX8aSuZa_content
attribs.current:
This is a minor spell that even most of the lowliest of fey can perform. You tap into your knowledge of magic and harness it to slightly nudge how you are perceived by others. You use your Arcana check in lieu of another skill to cause any of the following:

	Make yourself less noticeable and easily ignored. (Stealth)
	Be more alluring and attractive. (Persuade)
	Be more menacing and frightening. (Intimidate)

You must decide to use this ability before making any rolls. The effects last up to 5 minutes or until you decide to stop. You can only have one effect active at a time. If you fail a check while using this skill, the effect immediately ends and you cannot use it again on the same person for at least one day. To the observant eye, someone using Minor Glamour will have a glittered blurring effect over their face and form. The target of someone's Minor Glamour can use a Perception check (caster's spell DC) to notice this effect once a skill check has failed against them.

attribs.name: repeating_spell2_-KgYIgNZfk0VWX8aSuZb_content
attribs.current: Briefly surrounded by silvery mist, teleport up to 30 feet to an unoccupied space that you can see.

attribs.name: repeating_spell0_-KgYIgNZfk0VWX8aSuZc_content
attribs.current:
*Psionic Talent*

Communicate telepathically with one visible creature w/in 120 ft. Shared language (or any language) not needed for it to understand. Can allow to respond telepathically but must understand at least one language to communicate. Until start of next turn. Cannot communicate with unwilling creature.

attribs.name: repeating_spell0_-KgYIgNZfk0VWX8aSuZd_content
attribs.current:
*Psionic Talent*

Dissolve a held weapon into your body. Process is harmless to self and weapon. It is inaccessible as are its properties until weapon reappears. Only one weapon at a time. Reappears in space if unconscious or dead.

attribs.name: repeating_spell1_-KgYIgNaxPLX8oqFfLoy_content
attribs.current:
*Lesser Discipline (Celerity)*
*Cost:  1-5 psi point*

When rolling initiative, give self or one creature you can see w/in 60 ft +2 bonus on initiative PER POINT SPENT. If surprised, spend 1 point to no longer be surprised.

attribs.name: repeating_spell1_-KgYIgNaxPLX8oqFfLoz_content
attribs.current:
*Lesser Discipline (Celerity)*
*Cost:  2 psi points*

Increase speed by 30 ft until end of turn and do not provoke opportunity attacks this turn.

attribs.name: repeating_spell0_-KgYIgNaxPLX8oqFfLp-_content
attribs.current: While focused in this discipline, speed increases by 5 feet, advantage on initiative checks. If surprised, spend 1 psi point to no longer be surprised.

attribs.name: repeating_spell0_-KgYIgNbMglFDkgDa1Ww_content
attribs.current: While focused on this discipline, resistance to psychic damage. Also, able to suppress the effects of horror-marks. Within 15ft of self, use INT score as the scry DC.

attribs.name: repeating_spell1_-KgYIgNbMglFDkgDa1Wx_content
attribs.current:
*Lesser Discipline (Intellect Fortress)*
*Cost:  1-3 psi points*

As a reaction when you make Intelligence, Wisdom, or Charisma saving throw, gain +2 bonus to the save for each psi point spent. Can be used AFTER rolling but BEFORE applying the result.

attribs.name: repeating_spell0_-KgYIgNbMglFDkgDa1Wy_content
attribs.current:
*Psionic Talent*

Blast psychic energy at one visible creature. Intelligence saving throw or take 1d6 psychic damage. 

*If target takes any damage, can push it up to 10 spaces away from self.*

Damage increases: 2d6 (5th), 3d6 (11th), 4d6 (17th)

attribs.name: repeating_spell0_-KgYIgNcOf9fe5tw0Trs_content
attribs.current: Charge one nonmagical weapon or fist with psionic energy. Attacks made with it are considered MAGICAL and have +1 bonus to attack rolls and damage rolls.

attribs.name: repeating_spell1_-KgYIgNcOf9fe5tw0Trt_content
attribs.current:
*Lesser Discipline (Psionic Weapon)*
*Cost:  1 psi point*

Momentarily transform a weapon held into psionic energy. Next attack made with it requires no attack roll. Instead, target makes Dexterity saving throw against this discipline. Failed save, target takes attack's normal damage and suffers any effects. On success, half damage and no effects.

attribs.name: repeating_spell1_-KgYIgNcOf9fe5tw0Tru_content
attribs.current:
*Lesser Discipline (Psionic Weapon)*
*1-5 psi points*

When a target is hit with a melee weapon attack, increase damage. Extra 1d10 psychic damage per psi point spent.

attribs.name: repeating_trait_-KFL3ldCXVsq5ChLNP59_content
attribs.current: 2 for Order of the Awakened, 2 for level

attribs.name: repeating_trait_-KHfpbsTZT24LtKQaWaZ_content
attribs.current:
Focus the mind to read the psionic imprint left on an object. Hold and concentrate for 10 minutes, learn basic facts about it. Gain mental image from object's point of view, showing the last creature to hold the object, regardless of how long ago it was handled.

Also learn of any events that have occurred w/in 20 ft of the object within the past 24 hours. Events are perceived from the object's perspective (can see/hear events as if present, but no other senses).

Also, can embed an intangible psionic sensor w/in the object. Next 24 hrs, use an action to learn objects's location relative to self (distance and direction) and look at object's surroundings from its perspective as if present. Perception lasts until start of next turn.

attribs.name: repeating_trait_-KHfr35WrZibO2HWFMSv_content
attribs.current: Whenever you spend psi points on a psionic discipline of your order, regain hit points equal to INT mod if current hp total is half HP max.

attribs.name: repeating_trait_-KIKSwUZBMwIKOXBDt9V_content
attribs.current: Replace proficiency in WIS saving throws and apply the proficiency to STR, DEX, CON or CHA saving throws instead. The change lasts until the next short or long rest.

attribs.name: repeating_attack_-KFv1oysw8U21ysOqQhX_attack_string
attribs.current: +4 to hit, range 120 ft ft., one target.

attribs.name: repeating_attack_-KGKkgGJBce5gblxZv7A_attack_string
attribs.current: +4 to hit, reach 5 ft ft. or range 20/60 ft., one target.
